E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1138','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-13/a3521fb21b094c048b616d9707e093a0.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">参观净堡新村<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>日，县政协主席葛婷、副主席雷家兴、严嘉芬、赵季明及相关政协常委、委员一行<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>对我县城乡统筹和旅游发展情况进行了视察。副县长魏萍参加了视察活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">视察团一行先后来到渡普镇净堡新村、二乔公园、环湖公园、官桥新村油茶基地实地参观。净堡村依托湖北净宝农业发展有限公司，在该村进行迁村腾地项目建设，目前已建成顾家湾新村，为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>户村民建造了新房。走进具有浓郁徽派建筑特色的顾氏新村，政协委员们对这样精致又古朴的农村新貌赞叹不已，表示&ldquo;这不仅是新农村建设的成果，还是旅游发展的一处亮点。&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在即将完工的环湖公园，视察团一行走上雄风台，衬着三湖连江的波光，远眺嘉鱼城区，纷纷表示这样的景观让人赏心悦目，嘉鱼的旅游业发展前景看好。据了解，目前全长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.5</span>公里的环湖公园园建铺装工程已全面完工，现正在进行绿化、亮化及水电安装等收尾工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在随后召开的座谈会上，葛婷指出，近年来我县新农村建设风声水起，出现了净堡新村、四邑新村、界石新村等越来越多的亮点工程。相关部门要进一步做好统筹规划，进一步抓好新农村建设与旅游、与项目的结合，同时充分发挥能人、企业、基层党组织和群众的作用，加大检查、督办和奖评力度，促进我县城乡统筹和新农村建设工作再上新台阶。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">葛婷强调，我县旅游发展的良好势头来之不易，相关部门要加大对旅游发展的规划引导，加强宣传促销，注重文化产品、特产、纪念品等旅游产品的开发，加重对旅游环境的整治，将我县逐步打造成旅游强县。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">视察团还听取了县农办、县旅游局所作的关于我县城乡统筹、新农村建设和旅游发展的情况汇报，并提出了相关意见和建议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">魏萍对政协委员的建言献策表示感谢，她表示将尽快安排相关部门做好贯彻落实，促进全县城乡统筹和旅游工作更好更快发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-13/77b34493aa990298722695e0844a8bb1.jpg\\\\\" /></font></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">座谈会现场</font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1139','285','谢翔、陈功成','嘉鱼政务网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"DSC04373_副本_副本.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"500\\\\\" height=\\\\\"281\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-14/95bb41d24f42d9e52d1455864d613342.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"DSC04412_副本_副本.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"500\\\\\" height=\\\\\"281\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-14/151ed9ff20f2f5de946880d9e9e52afb.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">劳动现场</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">12</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>日下午，县发改局局长顾兴茂率全局机关干部到官桥镇跑马岭村周家塘参与塘堰护坡整治作业。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">劳动现场机声隆隆，挖掘机挥舞着长臂清理淤泥，发改局机关干部和官桥镇干部群众一起，拿起铁锹、土筐忙着整理沟渠，现场一片热火朝天的景象。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据悉，全县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动动员大会召开以来，县发改局迅速行动，第一时间为跑马岭村送去塘堰整治启动资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30000</span>元。目前，该村塘堰整治已完工<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>口，整治面积达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">43</span>亩，清淤沟渠达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">860</span>余米，土方量达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">36000</span>立方米，已组织劳力<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">180</span>余人，投入资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80000</span>余元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">整个工程竣工后，预计可以解决附近<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1100</span>余亩农田灌溉问题，极大地方便周边<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">170</span>余户农户的日常生产生活。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1140','285','熊铁山、鲁辉','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-14/2f4905261ddb67f0ff19533f63f90ccc.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n劳动现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>日，省国防科工办主任柳望春一行在县委常委、副县长许标的陪同下，来到潘家湾镇畈湖村深入开展&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">在村民明祖正家，柳望春一行与村两委班子和部分农户代表进行了座谈，详细了解了当前村民的生产生活情况和该村农田水利建设情况，并就创新农村管理体制机制、塘堰建设等进行了交流。随后，柳望春带领三十多名省科工办党员干部参加了畈湖村水渠清淤劳动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">在座谈中，柳望春指出，农村水利基础设施建设是今年三农工作的重中之重，省委、省政府深入贯彻落实中央<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>号文件精神，开展大水利建设，启动新一轮的&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，是巩固扩大上半年&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动成果的重要举措；是顺应群众期盼，言而有信，承而有诺，取信于民，解决实际问题的具体行动。他表示将尽最大努力帮助畈湖村解决好农田水利建设中存在的困题。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据悉，自年初&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动开展以来，省国防科工办在驻点村畈湖村先后投入<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">70</span>多万元，用于村民抗灾保收，基础建设，及帮助困难村民投资生产，用实际行动支持了驻点村的发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">潘家湾镇党委书记周亚澜，镇长涂秋意陪同参加了活动。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-14/55e294e8b4872df1a1238c1ac88fc110.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">与村民座谈<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1141','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-14/dea7fae777f7d364aa5732cbc05cba41.jpg\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">轮训班现场</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14</span>日，为期<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>天的全省乡镇党委书记轮训班（咸宁第二期）在嘉鱼县官桥八组开班。来自鄂东南<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>市的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">110</span>多名乡镇党委书记参加培训。省监察厅副厅长张家洪，咸宁市委组织部副部长王英，嘉鱼县委副书记、县长余珂出席开班仪式。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">张家洪指出，乡镇是国民经济最基本的运行单位，是我国现有的行政层级中最基础的一级，是党和政府在农村全部工作的基础。因此有针对性地开展科学发展主题培训，加强乡镇党委书记队伍建设是实现湖北跨越式发展的基础工程，是夯实基层基础的现实需要，更是建设高素质基层干部队伍的迫切需要。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">张家洪希望全体学员珍惜这次培训机会，端正学习态度，严格遵守学习纪律，集中精力听课，以良好的精神状态投入到学习中去。要学以致用，把理论知识和实践经验结合起来，转化为服务基层，服务群众的本领，为促进本地区经济社会跨越发展作出更大的贡献。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">余珂代表嘉鱼县委、县政府对全省乡镇党委书记轮训班在嘉鱼县官桥八组举办表示热烈欢迎，并就嘉鱼县近年来的经济社会发展情况向学员们作了介绍。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">余珂表示，嘉鱼县将以此次轮训为契机，深入贯彻落实中央、省委、市委在统筹城乡发展，强化基层党建等方面的一系列重大部署，结合&ldquo;三万&rdquo;和治庸问责工作，进一步加强基层干部教育培训和乡镇党委书记队伍建设，为打造湖北经济强县、长江临港新城提供坚强的组织保障。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据悉，本次乡镇党委书记轮训班设有分组讨论、专题报告、案例教学、现场参观等课程，并特邀省委党校、省社科院等单位的专家、教授为学员们进行专题讲座。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-14/9f7f8512f155fee9e50b3d79822a035f.jpg\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.8pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">轮训班现场</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1142','285','龙光辉','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">自开展新一轮&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动以来，县林业局组织&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作队，多次深入到官桥镇米埠村进行村情民情调查，协助该村制定塘堰修复计划，并筹措资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>万元支持该村兴修水利建设。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">该局利用今冬明春植树造林的大好时机，计划在该村塘堰沟渠周旁栽植沟、渠湾子林<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>万株，兴办造林示范点<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>亩，做到&ldquo;以树涵水、保土固塘、兴林富民&rdquo;。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据了解，官桥镇米埠村需要修复的塘堰<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>处，总计土方量<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>万<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">m<sup><font size=\\\\\"2\\\\\">3</font></sup></span>。目前该村已开挖塘堰<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>处，完成土方量<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7.5</span>万<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">m<sup><font size=\\\\\"2\\\\\">3</font></sup></span>，预计整体塘堰修复工程在今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月底前完工。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1143','285','陈才玮','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在实地察看新街镇蜀港村急需整治的塘堰和沟渠，并制定出整治计划和方案后，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，嘉鱼县司法局驻村工作队再次深入蜀港村开展&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，现场察看工程进展情况，确保工程如期圆满完工。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在蜀港村五组，县司法局局长章少阶对现场施工进行了检查指导，和村干部一起商讨了施工安排，以确保工程更好更快完成，他表示作为党员干部要急群众之所急，开展&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动要实实在在为百姓谋福利。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，县司法局在机关经费紧张困难的情况下，及时筹措</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元资金支持蜀港村清挖塘堰水利建设，解决该村多年吃水难的问题，受到了该村百姓的大力称赞。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1144','6','县委宣传部','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">截止<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14</span>日，全县绝大多数单位站在讲党性、讲政治的高度，不折不扣完成了党报党刊征订任务。城市规划执法局、一中、国土资源局、财政局等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>家单位主动扩大征订党报党刊覆盖面，超额完成征订任务，值得表扬。但仍有部分单位资金到位迟缓，还有个别单位迟迟没有行动，请相关责任人高度重视，切实加快进度，足额完成征订任务。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">附：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年度党报党刊发行工作情况通报<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">2012</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">年度党报党刊发行工作单位名单<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"