 lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">余珂要求，县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组在塘堰整治、沟渠清理方面要积极出资出劳；县水利部门要迅速行动，规划设计切实可行的塘堰整治方案；鱼岳镇要加强统筹协调和对时间进度、工程质量的检查督办；村组干部要发动群众积极参与，力争塘堰整治任务保质保量完成。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据了解，县政府办&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作组筹措资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>万元支持十景铺村兴修水利。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">经过调查摸底，该村共需疏通沟渠</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">1500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">米、扩容改造塘堰</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个。目前，沟渠已完成工程总量的三分之一，塘堰已开工建设</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-famil