E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1157','285','汪姝琴','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-15/50cdd41675455a4037eb94e660411b9e.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">塘堰整治现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 30pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">&ldquo;感谢总工会对我村的支持，当家塘工程进度才这么迅速。&rdquo;嘉鱼县陆溪镇印山村村支书尹立新告诉记者。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日，该镇印山村四组陈家坡塘整治进入煞尾工作，目前全村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>个组<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>口当家塘已基本完工。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 30pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据悉，印山村是县总工会此次三万活动的联系点，为贯彻落实县委县政府开展此次三万活动的精神，县总工会积极响应，迅速行动，提前谋划，召开了动员会，制定了活动方案，并成立了领导小组，加强领导，及时给村里送去了三万元塘堰整治启动资金。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 30pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">此次，县总工会还对印山村的塘库分布、病险塘堰情况进行了调查，研究塘堰整治方案，并向该村派驻了常驻工作组，发挥职能优势，帮助村组调查农民工情况，发动村组筹工筹劳，同时县总工会还将向有关部门争取项目支持，进一步帮助印山村&ldquo;搞好水利设施建设，每组修好一口当家塘&rdquo;这项民生工程，为今冬明春生产打好坚实基础。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 30pt; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1158','285','周新国','嘉鱼政务网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-15/421690f06e23552945bc5b0132bcf444.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">与村民一起座谈</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" day=\\\\\"10\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>日</st1:chsdate>，嘉鱼农行行长皮道勇带着<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4.32</span>万元现金（其中员工爱心款捐<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.32</span>万元），亲手交到了潘家湾镇官村党支部书记王冬生手中，用于该村沟渠修整及农田水利设施的改造。这是自今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月，该行在筹集资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.5</span>万元向该村帮扶后，又向官村捐出的一笔扶助款项。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">官村王书记表示：一定要将这笔资金用在村里的沟渠修整及农田设施改造上，以感谢嘉鱼农行全体干部员工对官村人民的关心和支持。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据悉，全县&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动动员会召开后，嘉鱼农行按照县委县政府的统一部署和要求，迅速派出&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作组，进村入户，调查摸底，掌握实情，制定实施方案，扎实开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动，切实帮助官村解决在农田水利基础建设方面的实际困难。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1159','285','县政府办','嘉鱼政务网','<p><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">14</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">上午，县长余珂率县政府办&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组来到鱼岳镇十景铺村，与当地村民一起挖沟清淤，用实际行动践行&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县政府办在此次&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动中，始终以&ldquo;挖塘堰，强基础，惠民生&rdquo;为主题，深入实地问民情解民忧，做到&ldquo;四快&rdquo;，即：传达落实快、组织专班快、进村入户快，资金到位快，争当&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的先锋队。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">一是传达落实快。</span><st1:chsdate year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" month=\\\\\"11\\\\\" day=\\\\\"30\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，嘉鱼召开全县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动暨农田水利基本建设动员大会后，县政府办立即召开会议，专题研究&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的有关事宜，对政府办&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动进行安排部署，使广大干部职工充分认识到&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动的重要性，增强了责任感和紧迫感。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">二是组织专班快。&ldquo;三万&rdquo;专题会议研究决定，成立县政府办&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动领导小组，由政府办副主任李黄金为组长，对&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的组织落实负总责，在</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作组的基础上，调整充实队员。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">三是进村入户快。&ldquo;挖塘堰&rdquo;活动开展以来，政府办主任余忠东，副主任李黄金等政府办领导率领工作队员多次来到十景铺村，深入调查实际情况，就相关工作问计于民、问需于民。先后</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">次在十景铺村两委成员及群众代表座谈，宣传政策，明确职责，研究制定塘堰整治和渠道疏浚的具体方案，确保&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动切实落实到位，真正做到惠民利民。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">四是资金到位快。&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动要迅速打开局面，资金是关键。为了进一步减轻村里负担，县政府办千方百计从单位经费中挤出</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，迅速送到基层。同时，政府办领导还在进一步筹措，以解决水利建设资金缺口难题。目前，沟渠已完成工程总量的三分之一，塘堰已开工建设</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，已经完工</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1161','6','丁闽鄂、徐雄、蔡明勇','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/ba32bc421aa95fefab4c36b2b0d1af30.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">考试现场</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: left\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span>日上午，嘉鱼县政协会议室正在举办一场别开生面的考试，全体机关干部聚精会神答着试题。这是县政协开展治庸问责活动的一个缩影。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据悉，考试内容为政协的各项制度，如《主席会议工作规划》、《常务委员会工作规则》、《专门委员会工作规划》等。目的是通过业务考试，着力提升政协干部的履职能力，进一步转变机关工作作风。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>月份以来，嘉鱼县全面启动治庸问责活动，为积极响应县委号召，县政协切实开展以&ldquo;治庸提能、治懒增效、治散提神、治软鼓劲&rdquo;为主题的治庸问责活动，制定了工作方案，成立了领导专班，坚持把思想教育、问题整改、责任追究、完善机制贯穿工作始终；突出抓好宣传、发动、自查整改、督查问责、总结提高四个环节，真正树立&ldquo;团结、和谐、创新、务实&rdquo;的政协形象。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n</span></div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1162','6','张大乐、夏正锋、张旭','咸宁日报','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/23e15e33e9eb22cbaf395f185e2a98ef.png\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">惠及自身利益的事，群众干起来劲头十足</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/9daed8721f5b6a80a68a11f2639c42fa.png\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">砌上护坡的塘将更加耐用</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/9870548cbf4c715c80c7750ed4024f90.png\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">干群齐上阵</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/ac3fea313a2b678f810cbbb0d5aca109.png\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队清沟挖渠</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp; <img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/d2d21fe8380afbf987674c8a8504e7cd.png\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">&ldquo;塘修好了，以后洗衣洗菜就方便多了。&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp; <img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/d1f985ca042f9fc4a78a5dbb4df6beaf.png\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">现代化机械助力开挖&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/35aa744fe5ef20e685570ced63b49550.png\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">一口塘承载着村民们许多回忆</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">初冬的咸宁，丝丝寒气弥漫在薄薄的晨雾中。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">13</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">日，咸安区马桥镇龙口村村支书冯家贵大清早就起床了，他今天要去<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>组查看门口塘的清淤扩建工程。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在去往门口塘的路上，几辆货车穿梭在乡村公路上，正在运送带有刺鼻气味的塘泥。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">来到门口塘，一台大型挖机正在作业，塘已经挖了一人多深，塘边围了一群村民，不时交头议论着。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">60</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">多岁的村民黄乃生一直生活在这口塘边，对这口塘颇有感情。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;记得小时候这塘水很清，到了上世纪<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80</span>年代末村民就没用过这塘里的水了。&rdquo;黄乃生回忆道。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;我<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1982</span>年嫁到这个村的时候，还在这口塘里洗过衣服，没过几年，这水就变臭了。&rdquo;从官埠桥镇嫁过来的郑海凤插话说。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;现在好了，政府出钱帮我们修水塘，以后我们<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">270</span>多口人洗衣洗菜就方便多了。&rdquo;老黄显得很兴奋。由于他们组还没通自来水，村民们每天要走一里多地去挑水，很不方便。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">记者来到浮山办事处龙潭村唐家堰，看见当地村干部正和村民们一起挑着塘泥。虽然天气寒冷，但不少村民的额头上渗出豆大的汗珠。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">40</span>年前，我还在生产队的时候挑过塘泥，一挑就是半天，现在身体不行了，挑几担就得歇歇。&rdquo;人群中，头发花白的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">75</span>岁村民詹琼娣干劲十足，格外显眼。今天村干部号召大家为修塘堰出份力，她也跑来凑一份子。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">记者来到嘉鱼县新街镇，见到了同样火热的场面。挖土机的轰鸣声，干部群众的吆喝声，抽水机的咕咕声汇成了一曲大兴水利的田园交响曲。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">县广电局&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队入驻新街镇晒甲山村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>组，一大早，工作队赶到西边桥当家塘，与当地群众一起清淤泥、挑土方。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;挖当家塘堰对我们这水源不足的地方是头等大事。&lsquo;三万&rsquo;工作队帮我们解决了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">400</span>多人的生活用水难题啊。&rdquo;该村党支部书记徐均平一边忙活一边对我们说道。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">不光要挖当家塘，村民们盼望解决的门前排水系统，也在嘉鱼农机局&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队的帮助下得以解决。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">该村毗邻长江，水源丰富，垸内水网纵横交错。&ldquo;以往一下雨，水没地方排，屋门口积水就有二三十厘米深，出门要趟水走，小孩的安全更是让人担心。多亏&lsquo;三万&rsquo;工作队帮助我们解决了问题，以后下雨再不用愁了。&rdquo;看着眼前日渐成型的排水沟，该村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>组村民殷祚年感激之情溢于言表。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">记者手记：让当家塘真正当家<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">今夏，一场百年一遇的大旱让我市农田水利建设的短板暴露无遗。因年久失修，&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;根本不当家，农民很无奈，庄稼只能望天收。建好&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;已迫在眉睫。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">全市新&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动已拉开大幕，计划在今冬明春建成上万口&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;。各级各地必须高度重视，迅速投入&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动，建好、管好、用好&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;，让&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;真正为农户、农田当好家。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">要科学选点，合理布局，编制好工程实施规划和方案，注重把&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;建设与调整农业产业结构、多种经营基地建设和解决&ldquo;饮水难&rdquo;结合起来，力争发挥最大效益。要创新投入机制，采取国家投入、地方配套、群众自筹、社会融资等多种方式，切实解决资金缺口。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">同时，要建立健全长效管理机制，尝试村级管理、民营合作、跨区统筹经营管理、租赁承包等长效管理模式，保证&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;生生不息。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1163','285','张大乐、夏正锋、张旭','咸宁日报','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/23e15e33e9eb22cbaf395f185e2a98ef.png\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">惠及自身利益的事，群众干起来劲头十足</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/9daed8721f5b6a80a68a11f2639c42fa.png\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">砌上护坡的塘将更加耐用</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/9870548cbf4c715c80c7750ed4024f90.png\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">干群齐上阵</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/ac3fea313a2b678f810cbbb0d5aca109.png\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队清沟挖渠</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp; <img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/d2d21fe8380afbf987674c8a8504e7cd.png\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">&ldquo;塘修好了，以后洗衣洗菜就方便多了。&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp; <img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/d1f985ca042f9fc4a78a5dbb4df6beaf.png\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">现代化机械助力开挖&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/35aa744fe5ef20e685570ced63b49550.png\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">一口塘承载着村民们许多回忆</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">初冬的咸宁，丝丝寒气弥漫在薄薄的晨雾中。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">13</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">日，咸安区马桥镇龙口村村支书冯家贵大清早就起床了，他今天要去<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>组查看门口塘的清淤扩建工程。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在去往门口塘的路上，几辆货车穿梭在乡村公路上，正在运送带有刺鼻气味的塘泥。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">来到门口塘，一台大型挖机正在作业，塘已经挖了一人多深，塘边围了一群村民，不时交头议论着。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">60</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">多岁的村民黄乃生一直生活在这口塘边，对这口塘颇有感情。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;记得小时候这塘水很清，到了上世纪<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80</span>年代末村民就没用过这塘里的水了。&rdquo;黄乃生回忆道。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;我<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1982</span>年嫁到这个村的时候，还在这口塘里洗过衣服，没过几年，这水就变臭了。&rdquo;从官埠桥镇嫁过来的郑海凤插话说。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;现在好了，政府出钱帮我们修水塘，以后我们<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">270</span>多口人洗衣洗菜就方便多了。&rdquo;老黄显得很兴奋。由于他们组还没通自来水，村民们每天要走一里多地去挑水，很不方便。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">记者来到浮山办事处龙潭村唐家堰，看见当地村干部正和村民们一起挑着塘泥。虽然天气寒冷，但不少村民的额头上渗出豆大的汗珠。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">40</span>年前，我还在生产队的时候挑过塘泥，一挑就是半天，现在身体不行了，挑几担就得歇歇。&rdquo;人群中，头发花白的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">75</span>岁村民詹琼娣干劲十足，格外显眼。今天村干部号召大家为修塘堰出份力，她也跑来凑一份子。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">记者来到嘉鱼县新街镇，见到了同样火热的场面。挖土机的轰鸣声，干部群众的吆喝声，抽水机的咕咕声汇成了一曲大兴水利的田园交响曲。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">县广电局&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队入驻新街镇晒甲山村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>组，一大早，工作队赶到西边桥当家塘，与当地群众一起清淤泥、挑土方。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;挖当家塘堰对我们这水源不足的地方是头等大事。&lsquo;三万&rsquo;工作队帮我们解决了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">400</span>多人的生活用水难题啊。&rdquo;该村党支部书记徐均平一边忙活一边对我们说道。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">不光要挖当家塘，村民们盼望解决的门前排水系统，也在嘉鱼农机局&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队的帮助下得以解决。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">该村毗邻长江，水源丰富，垸内水网纵横交错。&ldquo;以往一下雨，水没地方排，屋门口积水就有二三十厘米深，出门要趟水走，小孩的安全更是让人担心。多亏&lsquo;三万&rsquo;工作队帮助我们解决了问题，以后下雨再不用愁了。&rdquo;看着眼前日渐成型的排水沟，该村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>组村民殷祚年感激之情溢于言表。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">记者手记：让当家塘真正当家<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">今夏，一场百年一遇的大旱让我市农田水利建设的短板暴露无遗。因年久失修，&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;根本不当家，农民很无奈，庄稼只能望天收。建好&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;已迫在眉睫。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">全市新&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动已拉开大幕，计划在今冬明春建成上万口&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;。各级各地必须高度重视，迅速投入&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动，建好、管好、用好&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;，让&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;真正为农户、农田当好家。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">要科学选点，合理布局，编制好工程实施规划和方案，注重把&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;建设与调整农业产业结构、多种经营基地建设和解决&ldquo;饮水难&rdquo;结合起来，力争发挥最大效益。要创新投入机制，采取国家投入、地方配套、群众自筹、社会融资等多种方式，切实解决资金缺口。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">同时，要建立健全长效管理机制，尝试村级管理、民营合作、跨区统筹经营管理、租赁承包等长效管理模式，保证&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;生生不息。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1164','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/69d2899162961a391d7ed1d3d8cf9803.jpg\\\\\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">汇报会现场<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">16</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，县委常委、常务副县长熊武华带领考核组赴县财政局，就该局</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年落实党风廉政建设责任制及&ldquo;十个全覆盖&rdquo;工作情况进行考核。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊武华指出，县委、县政府高度重视党风廉政建设责任制工作，把惩治和预防腐败体系建设情况列为对党员干部考核的重要内容。作为财政系统的干部，更应该廉洁自律，以身作则；要以检查考核为契机，坚持标本兼治、综合治理、惩防并举、注重预防的方针，以落实党风廉政建设责任制为主线，建立健全符合财政实际的惩防体系，提升反腐倡廉建设水平。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县政协副主席、财政局局长刘平作了落实党风廉政建设及&ldquo;十个全覆盖&rdquo;工作自查报告。据介绍，今年以来，该局一手抓惩治违法违纪行为，一手抓健全廉政风险防控机制，不断提高财政反腐倡廉建设科学化水平，为各项工作顺利开展提供了有力保证。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">考核组通过召开座谈会，组织该局机关干部填写民主测评表，与个别干部谈话的方式，对该局党风廉政建设工作进行了全面的检查考核。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1165','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/d4c252107c3da03b58f9b23d5cb0c15a.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">开幕大会现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span>日，中国共产党咸宁市第四次代表大会隆重开幕。带着嘉鱼县人民的重托，由县委书记熊征宇为团长，县委副书记、县长余珂为副团长的嘉鱼县代表团成员共<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">43</span>人，以饱满的热情参加了会议。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">大会在雄壮的国歌声中开幕，县委书记熊征宇在主席台上就座，县领导余珂、魏朝东、袁秋明参加会议。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">市委书记黄楚平代表中共咸宁市第三届委员会在会上作了题为《全面推进科学跨越和谐发展为建成鄂南经济强市 共创幸福美好新咸宁而奋斗》的报告。《报告》指出，过去五年，是我市发展思路完善提升、改革开放不断深化的五年；是经济实现跨越发展、综合实力显著增强的五年；基础设施日益完善、城乡面貌变化巨大的五年；是社会事业加快发展、人民生活大幅改善的五年；是党的建设全面推进、执政能力不断增强的五年。今后五年我市要以科学发展为主题，以加快转变经济发展方式为主线，以推进新型工业化、新型城镇化、现代服务业和现代农业为抓手，大力实施&ldquo;工业崛起、旅游跨越、城乡统筹、生态持续、人才保障&rdquo;五大战略。在全面完成经济社会发展&ldquo;十二五&rdquo;规划的基础上，努力实现建成鄂南经济强市的目标，建设小康、生态、宜居、健康、和谐的幸福美好新咸宁。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">嘉鱼与会党代表认真听取了中共咸宁市第三届委员会的工作报告、中共咸宁市纪律检查委员会的工作报告，并对报告进行了深入讨论。此次大会为期<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>天，接下来与会党代表还将选举中共咸宁市第四届委员会、中共咸宁市纪律检查委员会。</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/1cb5fdd41b2d952ee32c034b09aed0e5.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇出席大会</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/a2e3bb35bb95c497dde4c8d0aa6a4df1.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">嘉鱼代表团出席大会</font></span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1166','285','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-16/578ca66868f155e83405c1390d564f07.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组清挖塘堰淤泥</span></div>\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">16</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日上午</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，县人大常委会主任李鹏谋率县人大&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组来到高铁岭镇临江村</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">组，与镇村干部群众一起挥舞铁锹，扩挖该村当家塘。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;对我们农民来说，&lsquo;三万&rsquo;活动真是件大实事、大好事啊！这塘挖好了，可就了却我们多年来的心愿了！&rdquo;临江村</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">组组长孙成焱告诉记者，这口塘名叫井上塘，开挖于上世纪</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">70</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年代中后期，承担着周边</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">200</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余亩农田的灌溉任务。由于开挖至今未曾清淤，加上部分村民图方便随意向塘里倾倒垃圾，当家塘库容量逐年减少，每逢抗旱时期灌溉用水更是供不应求。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县人大&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组了解情况后，积极与镇村干部、当地群众研讨农田水利基础设施改造方案，并在第一时间送去</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元资金及</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">吨水泥，用于该村塘堰沟渠的改造建设，并为村组塘堰更新改造作出了具体规划。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，临江村计划改造塘堰</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">处，计划筹资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元。截至目前，该村共投资改造塘堰</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">处，开挖土方量</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1.12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万立方米，清淤土方量</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7.98</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万立方米，浆砌块石</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">570</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">立方米</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。改造完成后，塘堰将新增蓄水量</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6.46</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万立方米，新增灌溉面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">965</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亩，受益人口达到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余人。</span></font><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"> <br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1167','6','','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日，由县委常委、宣传部长刘合权带队的考核组，到新街镇开展党风廉政建设责任制及&ldquo;十个全覆盖&rdquo;工作考核。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">刘合权指出，新街镇在落实党风廉政建设责任制工作中，思想上重视，措施到位，在抓组织领导、落实责任、学习教育、监督检查、制度建设等方面均取得了一定的成效。从具体的措施看，狠抓了责任分解、责任考核和建章立制工作，做到了职责明确；同时加强了对党员干部的教育，提高了廉洁自律的自觉性。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">刘合权要求新街镇继续抓好党风廉政建设。他强调，农村党风廉政建设直接关系到党的执政基础稳固，广大基层干部要切实履行党风廉政建设责任制，增强廉洁自律意识，管好自己的脑，脑要清醒，不要想入非非；管好自己的眼，眼要分清是非黑白，不要见利忘义；管好自己的耳，耳要听得见各方意见，多听组织的话，多听群众的话，不信谣传谣；管好自己的嘴，不讲不利于团结的话，不讲伤害群众感情的粗话、官话；管好自己的手，切记手莫伸，伸手必被捉；管好自己的腿，要脚踏实地，多为群众办好事、办实事。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">考核组听取了新街镇党委书记杨新武所作的述职述廉报告，查阅了该镇党风廉政工作相关资料，并对部分镇村干部进行了谈话。全体与会人员参加了对该镇党委班子的民主测评。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1168','6','熊铁山、李刚','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/ead2e0a1ef5495e3dfab5012d845cd3b.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">结业仪式现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span>日，全省乡镇党委书记轮训班（咸宁第二期）在官桥八组结业，省委组织部组织二处处长马锐，咸宁市委常委、组织部长龙良文，嘉鱼县委书记熊征宇，县委常委、组织部长袁秋明出席结业典礼。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">龙良文指出，这次培训班领导重视、学员认真、成效明显，达到了提高思想认识、增强群众观念、开阔眼界思路、学到有效方法的目的，收到了预期效果。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">龙良文强调，作为一名乡镇党委书记，要始终保持一个健康的心态，要学会知足、知道感恩、认真履责；要始终坚持一个原则，即民主集中制的原则，要在民主集中的基础上进行决策，在发扬民主中增进团结，在严于利己中增强合力；要始终牢记一个重大责任，常怀忧党之心、恪尽兴党之责，以更加奋发有为的精神状态推进党的建设；要始终秉持一种优良作风，大力弘扬求真务实、真抓实干，敢闯敢干、奋发有为，以人为本、亲民为民的作风。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">龙良文希望学员们回去后不辜负组织的期望，学用结合，知行合一，在乡镇这个大有可为的舞台上，始终保持蓬勃朝气、昂扬锐气、浩然正气，既坚定信心、勇挑重担，又脚踏实地、艰苦奋斗，为乡镇经济社会发展和社会主义新农村建设做出更大的贡献。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">马锐主持结业仪式，他指出，这次培训班层次高、规模大、内容多、形式活、效果好，充分体现了省委、省政府、省委组织部对换届后乡镇党委书记的高度重视，对乡镇党委书记的亲切关怀和殷切希望。他希望大家努力把学习成果转化为谋划工作的思路、加快发展的动力、服务群众的本领，带领广大干部群众进一步解放思想，抢 抓机遇，以改革创新精神和求真务实的作风，扎实苦干、锐意进取，推动乡镇又好又快发展。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">阳新县荆头山管理区党委书记王萍等学员代表就如何做好乡镇党委书记，切实履行好自己的职责谈了各自的认识和感受。</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-16/ddcd5d7761ced89a4984b28c725be249.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">结业仪式现场</span>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1169','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日上午，市委书记黄楚平、市委副书记丁小强等市四大家领导来到嘉鱼县代表团驻地，亲切看望了出席咸宁市第四次党代会的代表。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">黄楚平说，党代会是五年一次的盛会，是全市人民政治生活中的一件大事。开好本次党代会，对于总结全市过去五年工作、谋划未来五年发展，进一步凝聚全市人民智慧和力量，建设幸福美好新咸宁具有重要意义。他说，嘉鱼县拥有一支作风过硬的队伍，各项工作都走在全市前面，希望嘉鱼继续发扬好的传统和作风，与会代表要认真履行好代表职责，集思广益，凝心聚力，把未来五年的发展蓝图谋划好，把新一届市委、市纪委领导班子选举好，合力把此次大会开成一次务实、团结、鼓劲、 胜利的大会。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇表示，嘉鱼县代表团将以饱满的热情和严肃认真的态度开好大会，认真履行职责，积极建言献策，不辜负全市共产党员和广大人民的期望和重托。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1170','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span>日上午，中共咸宁市委第四次代表大会嘉鱼县代表团召开分团讨论，代表们重点讨论黄楚平同志在中共咸宁市委第四次代表大会上所作的《全面推进科学跨越和谐发展，为建成鄂南经济强市共创幸福美好新咸宁而奋斗》的报告及市纪委工作报告。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">市领导黄楚平、任振鹤、王远鹤、陈鸿池、胡毓军，及县领导熊征宇、余珂、魏朝东、袁秋明参加嘉鱼县代表团的讨论。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">市委书记黄楚平充分肯定了我县近几年来的发展成绩，认为我县具有一支作风过硬的干部队伍，顺利完成了县、镇、村换届选举工作，新一届四大家领导班子有活力、有战斗力，工作思路清晰。他要求，当前我县一定要抢抓各种发展机遇，不辜负市委、市政府的希望，认真领会大会精神，努力在加快建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城上下功夫，特别是路、桥、港、园区等一系列拟建和在建项目，都要做到早动手、早部署、早谋划。要把我县的旅游产业与海航集团、长鹿集团开发建设有机结合起来，进一步加快我县旅游产业发展步伐，力争使我县的旅游有特色、上档次。要加快现代农业的发展，不断创新城乡统筹、新农村建设发展模式，力争走在全市前列。为努力实现建成鄂南经济强市的目标，力争早日把咸宁建设成为小康、生态、宜居、健康、和谐的幸福美好新咸宁作出更大的贡献。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">市长任振鹤表示，五年来我县各项事业都取得了骄人成绩，农业从弱到强，工业从小到大，旅游业从无到有，主要经济指标高于全市各县区平均水平，发展不仅快而且好，为今后五年的发展奠定了良好的基础。目前我县面临着两圈一带、武汉新港等发展机遇，随着武深高速、长江大桥等一批重大项目的建设，我县的区位优势更加明显。任振鹤对我县未来发展提出了五个要求，即要巩固提升现代农业，加速推进县域经济，全面建设临港新城，加快培育旅游产业，不断提升普惠水平。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇表示，黄书记所作的报告鼓舞人心，催人奋进，不仅客观实在地总结了全市过去五年的工作，也为未来五年全市发展描绘了宏伟的蓝图，特别是报告中提出的建设幸福美好新咸宁的目标令人向往。他表示，我县将以项目建设为第一突破口，以改善民生为第一追求，以优化环境为第一要素，以保持稳定为第一责任，以党建为第一抓手，加快经济发展，普及惠民政策，打造农业特色，改善人民生活条件；做好城区总体规划，改善城乡面貌，着力打造全国旅游胜地；促进和谐发展，保障社会稳定；大力开展治庸问责，加强领导干部自身建设。不辜负市委市政府的厚望，不辜负全县党员群众的殷切希望，为早日实现湖北经济强县、长江临港新城的目标不断奋斗。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1171','285','汪姝琴、杨利','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;践行三万活动，送党报下乡，给农村基层带去党的声音。&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日，嘉鱼县城市规划执法局派驻&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组到官桥镇白湖寺村入户登记老党员、致富带头人名单和详细地址。据悉，该局结合&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作，开展送信息下乡活动，主动增订《咸宁日报》<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>份，送给村里的老党员、致富带头人。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;三万工作队真是我们的贴心人。&rdquo;该村支部书记周松林介绍，该局自&ldquo;三万&ldquo;活动启动以来，已累计投入近<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>万元，帮助村里兴修农田水利，整治当家塘堰，还结合该村实际情况，修建了连通<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>个组长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.2</span>公里的村级公路，帮助<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>家特困户进行危房改造，同时发挥职能优势，把该村纳入新农村建设规划，结合海航集团整体开发三湖连江规划修编进行村庄规划设计。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1172','285','聂莉','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-18/4a02250a35fbd8608499ca1014a91c6e.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: small\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">高铁岭镇机关党员干部与村民一起挖塘清淤</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17</span>日，高铁岭镇组织机关党员干部到广济堂村与群众一起挥锹劳动，为塘堰清淤出工出力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;得知要整治塘堰后，老百姓都很高兴、很支持，称赞党的政策好，塘堰改造是民心工程。&rdquo;该村支部书记杨红星介绍说，该村共有<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80</span>余口塘堰，是田间农作物的主要灌溉水源，其中有<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>口塘堰被列入整治范围内。由于年久失修，有的塘近三十年都没有整治过，淤积率高达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">40%</span>。在镇村组织下，特别是许多老党员、老干部充分发挥带头作用，许多村民也自发来到农田水利施工现场，主动投入到塘堰整修中。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据了解，&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动开展以来，高铁岭镇干部齐下乡、同劳动，共组织发动群众投工投劳<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>余人，开工塘堰<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>余处。其中，完成清淤和护坡塘堰<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>处，清淤土方<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80</span>万立方米，对塘堰四周修建浆砌块石挡土墙<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">800</span>余米，浆砌块石<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9360</span>立方米，坝面加宽平整。预估计，改造后塘堰蓄水量将达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">98.1</span>万立方米，灌溉面积扩大到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7229</span>亩，受益人口达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.1</span>万人。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1173','6','李发扬、江开群','咸宁日报','<p><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 16</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">日至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17</span>日，嘉鱼县代表团围绕中共咸宁第四次代表大会报告，畅所欲言。早日把嘉鱼建成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>湖北经济强县、长江临港新城<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>，是代表们谈论最多的话题。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 代表们一致认为，报告客观总结了近<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>年来取得的成绩，科学部署未来<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>年发展目标，报告高瞻远瞩，精髓在于大气魄、大手笔谋划发展，催人奋进。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>王远鹤代表说，报告提出建设幸福美好新咸宁，具体体现在五个咸宁建设。嘉鱼因水而灵，因江而贵。全县上下应抢抓发展机遇，科学定位，彰显发展特色，实施工业优先战略，抓园区、抓产业、抓品牌、抓人才保障。同时要处理好继承和创新的关系，坚持一张蓝图画到底。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>熊征宇代表说，报告多处提到嘉鱼的发展，咸嘉新城、长江大桥、百里蔬菜长廊、武深高速等项目的实施，必将推动嘉鱼更好更快发展。嘉鱼将围绕建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城的总体目标，加快构建<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>两区两城、两圈两带<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>发展格局。在经济强县、临港新城、旅游胜地、鱼米之乡和幸福家园等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>个方面下功夫，将嘉鱼建成人人向往之地。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>余珂代表说，全县将以实施工业倍增、农业转型、旅游跨越、城市宜居和交通畅通以及和谐惠民<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>六大工程<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>为载体，抓住工业发展第一要务，打响农业品牌，突破性发展特色旅游，狠抓民生保障等，努力把嘉鱼建设得更加幸福美好。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span>围绕建设湖北经济强县，黄绪江代表表示，将用良好的金融环境，为工业、旅游项目搞好服务，创新信贷产品、抵押担保等，破解中小企业融资难，他还建议成立金融办，加大力度培育上市公司，加大融资渠道。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>围绕建设长江临港新城，何晓山代表说，县里已启动城区高规格规划，高标准规划港口码头群、垂江经济带等，为新一轮大发展做铺垫。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>刘焰才代表说，嘉鱼将在文化产业上做大文章，将二乔文化产品融入旅游产业，通过引进文化创意产业等，促进嘉鱼文化大发展大繁荣。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 代表们还就突破性发展旅游业，打响农业品牌，加大民生保障等话题纷纷建言献策。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1174','284','周晓林、蔡娟','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: white; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;我们开展治庸问责，就是要重振干部形象、抖擞干部精神、激发全镇干部干事创业激情，既要干成事，又要干好事。&rdquo;近日，在全镇党委会议上，陆溪镇党委书记华红对全镇全体机关干部提出了这样的要求。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: white; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">今年以来，陆溪镇把&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;同各项工作紧密结合起来，以&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;为抓手统筹各项工作，把&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;作为检验各项工作的试金石，作为激活干部干事创业激情的催化剂，作为年终各项工作考核的&ldquo;指挥棒&rdquo;和&ldquo;风向标&rdquo;，唱响该镇各项工作的主旋律。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: white; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;塘名：细草塘；土方：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1230</span>立方；蓄水：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1850</span>立方；责任人：陈淑明&rdquo;，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18</span>日，在陆溪镇铜山村一组当家塘堰开挖现场，醒目的责任牌立在了塘堰边，见证着三万活动的实际成效。针对长鹿农庄项目正式签约嘉鱼，陆溪镇加强项目建设地周边村民征地搬迁宣传，群众矛盾纠纷调解、土地房屋丈量工作。在计生工作方面，开展计生突击月行动，对每一个育龄妇女落实一名党员干部包保，签定责任状，切实做好孕情包保监测，坚决杜绝政策内二孩及以上生育有出生无孕情。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: white; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&quot;</span>治庸问责<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&quot;</span>领导小组明确表示，工程上马之日，就是干部责任上肩之时，也是治庸问责之始。陆溪镇通过逐步推动治庸问责工作的常态化、制度化、规范化，呈现出高涨的士气，焕发出雷厉风行的工作作风和勇于担责、勇于担难的责任意识。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: white; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: white; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1175','285','江阳','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">13</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日下午，全国人大代表、武汉东湖学院董事长周宝生深入该校&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作组驻地，看望工作组的全体同志，并专题研究了此次挖塘堰工作的具体方案。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">一个星期以来，该校&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组在实地勘察和宣传动员之后，根据</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个村</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">29</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">口塘堰所在地的实际情况，制定了&ldquo;进村挖塘&rdquo;工作的具体方案，每位同志都不怕苦不怕累，在深入了解了各个村的实际情况以后，有针对性地展开了各项工作，并认真做好了工作日志。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在听取了学院工作组组长龙宗平的汇报后，周宝生说：&ldquo;省委省政府开展此次&lsquo;进万村挖万塘&rsquo;活动是一件惠民生、促发展的大好事，修建塘堰不仅可以解决群众生产、生活问题，也可以美化家园，更可以增产增效，这对社会主义新农村建设也是很有意义的事情。因此，武汉东湖学院的&lsquo;三万&rsquo;工作组一定要深刻认识此次&lsquo;三万&rsquo;活动的重要意义，明确工作任务，扎实推进挖塘堰工作&rdquo;。在详细了解了</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">29</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">口塘堰的具体情况以后，周宝生当即表示，要出资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">24</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元用于此次塘堰修建工程。根据</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">29</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">口塘堰的规模大小、修建标准和工程量的差异，每口塘堰都将获得不低于</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">元的补助。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">最后，周宝生还分别询问了工作组每位同志的工作情况，在肯定大家工作的同时，也希望大家能够借助此次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动实现自我锻炼和自我教育，同时也通过三个月的时间为驻地的老百姓做一两件好事、实事。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1176','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-19/644e7ab90669464027a032be64da4963.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">19</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，嘉鱼召开全县安全生产工作会议，总结回顾今年以来的安全生产工作，客观分析当前安全生产形势和存在的问题，并就&ldquo;两节&rdquo;前的安全生产工作进行安排部署。县领导余珂、李国光、李电波、饶自斌、许隆高、雷家兴出席会议。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县长余珂在会上作重要讲话，他指出，安全生产是经济发展和社会稳定的前提，必须充分认识做好安全生产工作的重要性。要克服麻痹思想，牢固树立忧患意识；克服侥幸心理，牢固树立风险意识；克服懒散作风，牢固树立责任意识。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余珂强调，安全生产重在防范，要强化措施，确保全县安全生产态势不断稳定好转。在日常监管上，落实安全生产工作例会、群防群治有奖举报等制度；在专项整治上，必须盯紧春运道路、水上交通、烟花爆竹、建筑施工等重点行业和重点领域，认真开展企业全面自查、部门专业检查和政府综合督查。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余珂要求，要落实责任，不断提高安全生产工作的监管监察能力。企业主要负责人要承担安全生产第一责任人的责任；各镇政府主要负责人要定期研究部署安全生产工作，解决重点难点问题；安监部门要依法履行安全生产综合监管职责；交警、消防、交通、教育、住建、药监、卫生、质监等部门，要加大对本行业领域的安全监管。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委副书记李国光主持会议，他要求各企业务必将安全工作牢记心头，以高度的责任感和使命感把各项工作任务和措施落到实处。再加措施，再鼓干劲，促进全县安全生产形势进一步稳定好转，给全县人民交一份满意的答卷。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">副县长许隆高对全县下阶段的安全生产工作进行了安排部署。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县安监局局长雷跃通报了全县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年安全生产工作情况。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1177','285','张旭','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">&ldquo;大家快来看啊，排水沟修到家门口来啦。&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span>日，嘉鱼县牌洲湾镇新洲村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>组，伴着轰隆隆的机器声，村民们竞相走出家门，一睹为快。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">挖土机挥舞着巨臂忙掘沟，&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队队员抡起锄头紧随其后忙修整。&ldquo;能够帮助村里解决实际困难，让广大群众在&lsquo;三万&rsquo;活动中真正得到实惠，我们干起来也来劲。&rdquo;县农机局&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队队长来兰贵挽起袖子，忙得不亦乐乎。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">牌洲湾镇毗邻长江，水源丰富，牌洲湾垸内横向主渠<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16.5</span>公里，纵向主渠<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">22</span>条<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">85</span>公里，水网纵横交错，客观条件决定了这里的&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动应以沟渠疏通为主而非塘堰整治，自然而然，泵站维修，沟渠套洗成了新洲村水利建设的重要内容。据该村党支部书记殷先山介绍，为利用好这次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的良好机遇，村里充分听取民意，让村民代表们决定上报哪些项目，最终经过县、镇、村共同讨论，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">480</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">米门前排水沟疏通、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1600</span>米下新渠清淤等被确定为该村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>个组各自的&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动项目。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &ldquo;以往一下雨，水没地方排，屋门口积水就有二三十厘米深，出门要趟水走，小孩的安全更是让人担心，多亏&lsquo;三万&rsquo;工作队下来帮我们解决问题，以后下雨都不用愁了。&rdquo;看着眼前日渐成型的排水沟，该村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>组村民殷祚年感激之情溢于言表。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">这一边，新洲村在忙着疏通沟渠；那一边，新街镇晒甲山村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>组，县广电局&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队则与当地村民一起挖淤泥、挑土方，忙着改造西边桥当家塘堰。&ldquo;以往洗衣服都要跑一里地，麻烦得很咯。&rdquo;&ldquo;挖当家塘堰对我们这水源不足的地方可是头等大事&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;大家你一言，我一语地打开了话匣子，边干活边讨论，场面热火朝天。现场，晒甲山村党支部书记徐均平告诉记者，该工程目前已完成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">90%</span>，修复完成后蓄水量可达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5000</span>立方，全组<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">400</span>多人的生产生活用水问题可得到解决。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">据了解，此次嘉鱼县将&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动与农田水利基本建设结合起来，整治建设类型根据各村组实际需要分为塘堰整治、泵站维修、沟渠套洗、桥梁维修四大类，全县因地制宜兴水利。截至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月上旬，塘堰整治开工<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">209</span>口、泵站维修（新建）启动<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>个、沟渠套洗动工<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">142</span>条、桥梁维修动工<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>处。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1178','6','admin','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">历时<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>天的中国共产党咸宁市第四次代表大会，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18</span>日在咸宁市会议中心胜利闭幕，大会主席团常务委员会成员黄楚平、任振鹤、丁小强、胡建华、龙良文、陈树林、王远鹤、黄剑雄、夏亚灵、黄宏贵、董国祥在主席台前排就座，我县领导熊征宇、余珂、魏朝东、袁秋明参加了会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">在热烈的掌声中，黄楚平发表了重要讲话。他说，这次会议全面总结了市第三次党代会以来的成绩和经验，深入分析了面临的形势和存在的问题，确定了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>早日建成鄂南经济强市、共创幸福美好新咸宁<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>的战略思路、奋斗目标、重大战略和重点任务，选举产生了新一届市委和市纪委。大会审议通过的第三届市委工作报告，集中了全市广大党员干部和人民群众的智慧，充分体现了科学发展观的要求，体现了省委、省政府对咸宁发展的战略定位，表达了全市人民追求幸福生活的共同愿望，展示了咸宁未来发展的美好前景，是今后五年全市工作的纲领性文件。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">黄楚平指出，蓝图已经绘就，目标已经明确，核心在于实干，关键在于落实。我们要始终保持蓬勃朝气、旺盛豪气和昂扬锐气，以扎实的作风和勤奋的工作，全面贯彻落实党代会精神，努力把党代会绘就的壮丽蓝图变成美好的现实。建设幸福美好新咸宁，必须始终坚持科学跨越和谐发展，必须始终保持奋发有为的精神状态，必须始终依靠人民群众的力量，必须始终坚持党的领导。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">黄楚平最后说，时代赋予我们神圣的使命，人民寄予我们殷切的希望。让我们紧密团结在以胡锦涛同志为总书记的党中央周围，在省委、省政府的正确领导下，万众一心，奋发图强，为全面推进科学跨越和谐发展，早日建成鄂南经济强市、共创幸福美好新咸宁而不懈奋斗，以优异成绩迎接党的第十八大和省第十次党代会胜利召开！<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1179','285','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-20/eaf296ba2937dd2e8afbee843ebb0a5f.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队挖塘现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">干群挥锄铲泥，挖掘机卧塘清淤，<st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"20\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日</st1:chsdate>，在嘉鱼县新街镇马鞍山村四组的当家塘堰整修现场，一派热火朝天的景象。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">来自市纪委、市住建委和嘉鱼县委宣传部的&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队队员与村民一起，正在将塘堰中央还没有清理好的淤泥用扁担、箩筐挑到塘堰周围的护坡上。&ldquo;来，你铲土，我来挑。&rdquo;虽然刚刚被机器挖过的塘堰底部淤泥还没有干，但是&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队队员们都争着抢着到塘堰下面去挖泥挑土，干劲十足。 <span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据了解，这口正在进行整修的塘堰是马鞍山村四组的一口当家塘，主要用于周边菜地的灌溉和抗旱，由于年久失修，淤泥堵塞，导致无法发挥蓄水的作用。该村四组组长刘分介绍说：&ldquo;以前这塘很小而且浅，装不了水，菜地里要水的时候只能接很长的管子到长江里去抽水，不仅费时费力，有时还根本抽不上水。&rdquo; <span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">在此次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动中，市、县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队帮助该村将此塘进行了扩大面积和加大深度，蓄水量将达到<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"1\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"30000\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"立方米\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>万立方米</st1:chmetcnv>，能满足周边<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>多亩田地的用水需要。&ldquo;这塘修好了好处多得很呢，不仅方便灌溉、抗旱，平常收菜卖菜时，还能就近洗菜，菜干净了才卖的好啊。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>村里一位菜农也高兴地说道。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据了解，市、县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队此次共为该村筹资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18</span>万元，支持该村进行水利设施建设，共为该村整修当家塘堰<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>口，清修渠道<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3000</span>余米，维修泵站<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>座。同时借助此次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，市纪委、市住建委还组织干部职工对该村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>户计划生育困难户进行结对帮扶，为每户送去<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>元慰问金，将关怀送到村民家里，将温暖送进村民心中。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">市纪委副书记张远森、陈剑、熊亚平，市住建委主任李华平，县委常委、县委宣传部长刘合权参加活动。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1180','284','杨金琪、黄念','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;把治庸问责工作常态化，把治庸督查经常化，把治庸监管制度化。&rdquo;这是渡普镇党委书记余洪煌在全镇治庸问责工作动员会上提出的要求。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">近日，渡普镇治庸问责领导小组对镇直各部门、各村（居委会）治庸问责工作开展情况进行了一次全方位明察暗访。检查结果显示，各单位工作人员认真服务、秩序井然，没有发现玩游戏、迟到、早退、旷工等现象。各村也都在积极进行计划生育&ldquo;三查四术&rdquo;。镇区街道，城管、环卫、土管及镇机关干部联合拆违，整治环境，为公路刷黑做准备。同时，结合&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动开展情况，各村当家塘堰及水利工作进展迅速，全镇上下&ldquo;庸&rdquo;&ldquo;懒&rdquo;&ldquo;脱&rdquo;现象大有好转，呈现出一派欣欣向荣景象。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据悉，自<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日早上该镇召开治庸问责工作动员会后，当晚镇党委趁热打铁，又组织全体机关干部深入学习了县委书记熊征宇、县纪委书记魏朝东及县组织部长袁秋明关于治庸问责工作的讲话。镇直各部门、各村（居委会）均成立了治庸问责领导小组、制定了实施方案，镇机关、学校、派出所布置了学习专栏。全镇上下已掀起治庸问责风暴。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
