New Roman\\\\\">15</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元的湖北三木畈湖涂料工业园项目签约仪式在潘家湾镇隆重举行。县领导熊征宇、余珂、李国光、许隆高，三木集团董事长刘洪林出席签约仪式。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，三木集团是江苏省百强民营企业，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2007</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年荣登中国制造业</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">强，是专业从事涂料用树脂（溶剂）和树脂原料研发、生产以及配套铜和电缆生产与销售的大型集团企业，在行业中素有&ldquo;涂料用树脂王国&rdquo;之称。此次，该集团经过充分的市场调研和科学周密的分析论证，选址在我市唯一一家市级化工专业园&mdash;&mdash;潘家湾畈湖化工工业园投资兴业，建设三木畈湖涂料工业园。该项目固定资产总投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，占地</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亩。项目分三期建设，预计建成投产后可实现年税收约</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，吸纳</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">人就业。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇表示，三木畈湖涂料工业园项目的落户，将对畈湖工业园的发展壮大，提档升级产生决定性的作用，也将会大力促进嘉鱼经济快速发展，为我们早日建成湖北经济强县做出新的贡献。他要求各相关职能部门全力支持三木工业园的建设，提供一流的工作效率，提供最优质的服务，营造最优越的建设环境。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县长余珂说，今年我县围绕打造六大产业集群，举全县之力招商引资，在项目投资和建设过程中，我们将严格履行承诺，开辟&ldquo;绿色通道&rdquo;和&ldquo;直线跑道&rdquo;，力争项目早日开工、早日投产达效。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委副书记李国光主持签约仪式。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县长余珂、三木集团董事长刘洪林、潘家湾镇党委书记周亚澜签订项目投资合同书。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">国土、环保等职能部门负责人作了表态发言。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1182','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-20/4720c8064b631b397db750e7aa8fdbe9.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">培训班开班仪式现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;我将好好珍惜这次培训机会，掌握一技之长，争取顺利就业、努力创业！&rdquo;</span><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"20\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，在嘉鱼县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年退役士兵创业培训班开班仪式上，退役士兵代表胡杰说道。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">副县长魏萍出席开班仪式，她要求承训机构要严格教育管理，确保退役士兵培训质量，提高其创业的能力，引导退役士兵自谋职业和自主创业；广大退役士兵要珍惜学习机会，勤奋学习，掌握创业本领。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">时下正值老兵退伍，退伍士兵返乡后的就业问题成了全社会关注的&ldquo;焦点&rdquo;。为了提升退伍士兵的就业能力，增强其就业信心，鼓励其自主创业，嘉鱼县组织开展对退伍士兵进行为期两个月的免费职业技能培训。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">培训内容不仅包括市场营销、创业理财、企业管理、经济法规等理论知识，还设置有计算机应用、汽车维修与驾驶、电子电工技术、数控技术、美容美发、旅游与酒店管理、电焊技术、机械加工等实用技能。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">同时，县人社局、民政局等部门还将为退伍士兵开展一个月的免费咨询指导和后续支持服务，并将优先推荐就业、支持创业。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<div><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p><o:p></o:p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-20/d1a921a7b1ef64bc909eb6727658d3fb.jpg\\\\\" /></font></o:p><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">退伍士兵们在认真听课</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><br />\r\n</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1183','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-20/af754f84328b4fdcbcfbc3eeea4e86b1.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n培训班现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"20\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日下午</st1:chsdate>，嘉鱼县农村党组织书记培训班在县委党校开班。县委书记熊征宇，县委副书记李国光，县委常委，组织部长袁秋明出席了开班仪式。来自全县各个乡镇的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">130</span>多位乡镇组织委员、村党组织书记和大学生村官参加了培训。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">熊征宇说，农村党组织书记是基层组织建设、凝聚党员群众的&ldquo;顶梁柱&rdquo;，是贯彻惠农政策、推进农村工作的&ldquo;主心骨&rdquo;，是发展农村经济、带领群众致富的&ldquo;领头雁&rdquo;，是密切党群关系、维护社会稳定的&ldquo;连心桥&rdquo;，因此这次培训意义重大，对促进农村经济快速发展，保持农村社会和谐稳定具有很重要的作用。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">熊征宇重点强调了农村党组织书记在认识、定位、履职等三方面的工作。他说，开展农村党组织书记培训是推动嘉鱼科学发展、跨越发展战略之举，大家务必要思想统一；农村党组织书记在建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城中作用非常重要，大家要定位正确；做一名优秀的农村党组织书记是适应发展之需、群众所盼，大家要尽职尽责。他希望大家珍惜这次学习机会，端正学习态度，集中精力，多学、多看、多交流，不断提高自身素质，不辜负党和广大人民群众的重托，在农村这个大舞台上大显身手，为建设和谐美好新农村，实现嘉鱼经济社会又好又快发展做出积极的贡献。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">李国光主持开班仪式，他要求全体学员认真学习，提高本领，将此次培训班的精神带回去，及时向广大基层党员干部群众传达，为我县加快建设湖北经济强县，长江临港新城作出新的更大的贡献。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据悉，这次培训班学习的内容涉及到党的十七届六中全会精神、基层社会管理、党风廉政建设、新农村建设、依法整治&ldquo;两违&rdquo;行为、基层信访工作等。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-20/1171919d5974002a41c03c1c5059f6f6.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">培训班现场</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1184','285','陈功成','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">整治当家塘堰、造福千家万户。自嘉鱼县&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动开展以来，官桥镇党委政府高度重视、及时动员、周密部署，迅速在全镇掀起了&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的热潮。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">各村按照县、镇&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的相关要求，科学拟定并上报整治计划，精心挑选施工队伍，积极组织民工投工投劳。县驻村&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作队、全体联村干部及村&ldquo;两委&rdquo;干部全程跟踪进行现场指导，确保工程进度和质量。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">截至目前，全镇<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>个村已上报（计划）整治塘堰数<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>口，已开工<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">44</span>口，完工<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">47</span>口，总计投入资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">120</span>万元，民工<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13000</span>人，预计全部工程完工后，可实现蓄水<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">150</span>万立方，解决<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">38000</span>余亩农田灌溉问题。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1185','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-20/eaf296ba2937dd2e8afbee843ebb0a5f.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队挖塘现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">干群挥锄铲泥，挖掘机卧塘清淤，<st1:chsdate isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"20\" month=\"12\" year=\"2011\" w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>日</st1:chsdate>，在嘉鱼县新街镇马鞍山村四组的当家塘堰整修现场，一派热火朝天的景象。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">来自市纪委、市住建委和嘉鱼县委宣传部的&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队队员与村民一起，正在将塘堰中央还没有清理好的淤泥用扁担、箩筐挑到塘堰周围的护坡上。&ldquo;来，你铲土，我来挑。&rdquo;虽然刚刚被机器挖过的塘堰底部淤泥还没有干，但是&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队队员们都争着抢着到塘堰下面去挖泥挑土，干劲十足。 <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">据了解，这口正在进行整修的塘堰是马鞍山村四组的一口当家塘，主要用于周边菜地的灌溉和抗旱，由于年久失修，淤泥堵塞，导致无法发挥蓄水的作用。该村四组组长刘分介绍说：&ldquo;以前这塘很小而且浅，装不了水，菜地里要水的时候只能接很长的管子到长江里去抽水，不仅费时费力，有时还根本抽不上水。&rdquo; <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">在此次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动中，市、县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队帮助该村将此塘进行了扩大面积和加大深度，蓄水量将达到<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" tcsc=\"1\" numbertype=\"1\" negative=\"False\" hasspace=\"False\" sourcevalue=\"30000\" unitname=\"立方米\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>万立方米</st1:chmetcnv>，能满足周边<span lang=\"EN-US\">1500</span>多亩田地的用水需要。&ldquo;这塘修好了好处多得很呢，不仅方便灌溉、抗旱，平常收菜卖菜时，还能就近洗菜，菜干净了才卖的好啊。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>村里一位菜农也高兴地说道。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">据了解，市、县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队此次共为该村筹资<span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span>万元，支持该村进行水利设施建设，共为该村整修当家塘堰<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>口，清修渠道<span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span>余米，维修泵站<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>座。同时借助此次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，市纪委、市住建委还组织干部职工对该村<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>户计划生育困难户进行结对帮扶，为每户送去<span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span>元慰问金，将关怀送到村民家里，将温暖送进村民心中。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">市纪委副书记张远森、陈剑、熊亚平，市住建委主任李华平，县委常委、县委宣传部长刘合权参加活动。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1186','6','张姝、罗阳春','中国嘉鱼网','<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhaoshangyinzi/zhaoshangdongtai/2011-12-20/ed75641ac1ecb76d818f2f50d68eedd0.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhaoshangyinzi/zhaoshangdongtai/2011-12-20/b60bac53181761f2ebf8a0a5f0494a62.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">签约仪式现场<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，总投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元的湖北三木畈湖涂料工业园项目签约仪式在潘家湾镇隆重举行。县领导熊征宇、余珂、李国光、许隆高，三木集团董事长刘洪林出席签约仪式。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，三木集团是江苏省百强民营企业，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2007</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年荣登中国制造业</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">强，是专业从事涂料用树脂（溶剂）和树脂原料研发、生产以及配套铜和电缆生产与销售的大型集团企业，在行业中素有&ldquo;涂料用树脂王国&rdquo;之称。此次，该集团经过充分的市场调研和科学周密的分析论证，选址在我市唯一一家市级化工专业园&mdash;&mdash;潘家湾畈湖化工工业园投资兴业，建设三木畈湖涂料工业园。该项目固定资产总投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，占地</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亩。项目分三期建设，预计建成投产后可实现年税收约</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元，吸纳</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">人就业。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇表示，三木畈湖涂料工业园项目的落户，将对畈湖工业园的发展壮大，提档升级产生决定性的作用，也将会大力促进嘉鱼经济快速发展，为我们早日建成湖北经济强县做出新的贡献。他要求各相关职能部门全力支持三木工业园的建设，提供一流的工作效率，提供最优质的服务，营造最优越的建设环境。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县长余珂说，今年我县围绕打造六大产业集群，举全县之力招商引资，在项目投资和建设过程中，我们将严格履行承诺，开辟&ldquo;绿色通道&rdquo;和&ldquo;直线跑道&rdquo;，力争项目早日开工、早日投产达效。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委副书记李国光主持签约仪式。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县长余珂、三木集团董事长刘洪林、潘家湾镇党委书记周亚澜签订项目投资合同书。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">国土、环保等职能部门负责人作了表态发言。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1187','6','黄念','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日下午，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东，副县长魏萍来到渡普镇调研&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动开展情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">魏朝东一行来到东湖闸峡港河清淤现场，详细询问了清淤情况，得知东湖闸是斧头湖与峡港河相连的重要闸口，每年旱涝季节发挥着巨大作用，他强调一定要把东湖闸维修好，峡港河清淤彻底，并现场提出建议：规划闸前拦水坝，深挖拓宽闸口附近河道，搞好护坡，安装拦污纱，阻止水草等杂物堵塞河道。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在烟墩村五组蔡许塘，看到正在清淤的塘堰初现规模，魏朝东一再嘱咐要抢抓晴天，加快进度。站在渡普桥上，魏朝东仔细了解了金水河清淤以及两岸护坡规划情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">魏朝东对渡普镇党委、政府开展&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动早部署早行动、合理规划表示肯定，同时强调要因地制宜，量力而行，抢抓时机，搞好这项民生工程，争取为明年的农业生产提供强有力保障。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">目前，渡普镇塘堰整修、沟渠清淤、泵站维修、涵闸整修、桥梁兴修五大类水利建设项目已完成塘堰整修<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>口、沟渠清淤<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14</span>处、泵站维修<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>处。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县政府办副主任方明祥、县农办主任耿协刚、县水利局局长夏毅等一行陪同调研。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
