: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">目前，渡普镇塘堰整修、沟渠清淤、泵站维修、涵闸整修、桥梁兴修五大类水利建设项目已完成塘堰整修<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>口、沟渠清淤<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>处、泵站维修<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>处。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">县政府办副主任方明祥、县农办主任耿协刚、县水利局局长夏毅等一行陪同调研。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1189','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">昨日上午，从在北京召开的全国精神文明建设表彰大会上传出喜讯：嘉鱼县城被中央文明委命名为第三批全国文明村镇。嘉鱼是此次评选中咸宁市唯一入选的县城。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2005</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年来，我县开展了三次&ldquo;省级文明县城&rdquo;活动，也连续蝉联荣誉称号，并先后成功创建全国、省、市、县文明单位</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余个，形成了一套宝贵的创建经验，建立了一套科学有效的创建机制，取得了丰硕的创建成果。同时，通过争创&ldquo;省级文明县城&rdquo;、&ldquo;省级卫生县城&rdquo;、&ldquo;省级园林县城&rdquo;等活动，基础设施不断完善，大街小巷明显改善，市政基础设施、公共交通、医疗卫生、公共绿地等重点区域和关键环节达标水平明显提升，居民幸福指数日益提高。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">作为蔬菜之乡、黄金之乡、螃蟹之乡、水产大县、绿化大县、二乔故里的诗经嘉鱼，近年来累计投资近</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，完成城区</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">条主次干道的扩建、延伸和改造；投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元对发展大道、人民大道、沿湖大道、迎宾大道全线刷黑；投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元实施了环三湖连江截污工程和环梅懈湖排污管网铺设工程。同时，启动武汉至嘉鱼一级公路建设，实施城区外环公路联网；全面开展老城区改造，将沙阳大道、凤凰大道路面全线改造、刷黑，人行道高标准翻修，改善支街小巷设施；投资开发山湖温泉，建设人民公园、二乔公园、三湖连江沿湖景观带&hellip;&hellip;发展环境不断优化，县域经济实力明显增强，一个最宜投资、最宜创业、最宜人居、最宜发展的嘉鱼已具雏形。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在文明创建工作中，我县始终坚持将群众性精神文明创建工作作为重点，着力提高市民素质，大力开展对城区卫生、交通秩序和&ldquo;窗口&rdquo;单位服务环境的整治，切实完善社区管理与服务，丰富居民文化生活。同时，突出抓好了提升干部职工文明素质的单位文明创建工作，着力开展了满足市民精神需要的广场文化活动，重点进行了新农村建设的文明村镇评比、&ldquo;文明创建进农家&rdquo;等活动，加强了未成年人思想道德素质建设，从老百姓普遍关注、反映强烈、广泛受益的事情抓起，确保群众共享文明成果并从中得到实惠，赢得广大群众的热情参与和对文明创建的一致好评。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，在此次表彰中，田野集团股份有限公司（本部）也获得第三批全国文明单位称号。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1190','268','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">昨日上午，从在北京召开的全国精神文明建设表彰大会上传出喜讯：嘉鱼县城被中央文明委命名为第三批全国文明村镇。嘉鱼是此次评选中咸宁市唯一入选的县城。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2005</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年来，我县开展了三次&ldquo;省级文明县城&rdquo;活动，也连续蝉联荣誉称号，并先后成功创建全国、省、市、县文明单位</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">30</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">余个，形成了一套宝贵的创建经验，建立了一套科学有效的创建机制，取得了丰硕的创建成果。同时，通过争创&ldquo;省级文明县城&rdquo;、&ldquo;省级卫生县城&rdquo;、&ldquo;省级园林县城&rdquo;等活动，基础设施不断完善，大街小巷明显改善，市政基础设施、公共交通、医疗卫生、公共绿地等重点区域和关键环节达标水平明显提升，居民幸福指数日益提高。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">作为蔬菜之乡、黄金之乡、螃蟹之乡、水产大县、绿化大县、二乔故里的诗经嘉鱼，近年来累计投资近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">5</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿元，完成城区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">5</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">条主次干道的扩建、延伸和改造；投资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">5000</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">万元对发展大道、人民大道、沿湖大道、迎宾大道全线刷黑；投资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1000</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">万元实施了环三湖连江截污工程和环梅懈湖排污管网铺设工程。同时，启动武汉至嘉鱼一级公路建设，实施城区外环公路联网；全面开展老城区改造，将沙阳大道、凤凰大道路面全线改造、刷黑，人行道高标准翻修，改善支街小巷设施；投资开发山湖温泉，建设人民公园、二乔公园、三湖连江沿湖景观带&hellip;&hellip;发展环境不断优化，县域经济实力明显增强，一个最宜投资、最宜创业、最宜人居、最宜发展的嘉鱼已具雏形。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">在文明创建工作中，我县始终坚持将群众性精神文明创建工作作为重点，着力提高市民素质，大力开展对城区卫生、交通秩序和&ldquo;窗口&rdquo;单位服务环境的整治，切实完善社区管理与服务，丰富居民文化生活。同时，突出抓好了提升干部职工文明素质的单位文明创建工作，着力开展了满足市民精神需要的广场文化活动，重点进行了新农村建设的文明村镇评比、&ldquo;文明创建进农家&rdquo;等活动，加强了未成年人思想道德素质建设，从老百姓普遍关注、反映强烈、广泛受益的事情抓起，确保群众共享文明成果并从中得到实惠，赢得广大群众的热情参与和对文明创建的一致好评。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">据悉，在此次表彰中，田野集团股份有限公司（本部）也获得第三批全国文明单位称号。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\"><o:p><font face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1191','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-21/b19bc6ecbe9819ac3e3d5259a2e717e8.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在中能锂电视察<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">21</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，嘉鱼县第十七届人民代表大会常务委员会第一次全体会议召开。县人大常委会主任李鹏谋，副主任谢望松、秦建平、曾祥坤、李电波、贺隆君、戴书萍出席会议，县委常委、组织部长袁秋明，副县长许隆高，县法院院长赵志诚、检察院检察长邓佛围列席会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议听取和审议了县政府关于工业园区及一区多园建设情况的报告；听取和审议了县政府关于全县农田水利基本建设情况的报告；听取和审议了县政府关于全县城乡统筹发展试点工作和新农村建设情况的报告。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议提出了《关于提请审议操文卿同志任职的议案》；县委常委、组织部长袁秋明作了关于人事任免的说明；操文卿作了拟任职发言。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">根据现场投票表决结果，县人大常委会决定任命操文卿同志为嘉鱼县公安局局长，并向其颁发了任命书。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会前，县人大组织与会人员赴中能锂电、联乐集团、峰华科技、恒鑫脚手架、金亮织带等企业，及官桥村新农村项目建设现场进行了视察。县人大常委会组成人员充分肯定了县政府在工业园建设、新农村建设等方面取得的成绩，并对这些工作给予了很多意见和建议。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">李鹏谋指出，近年来，我县在&ldquo;一区多园&rdquo;建设、新农村建设和水利建设上取得了可喜的成绩，为全县经济社会发展做出了重要贡献。希望县政府及相关工作部门认真研究、积极吸纳人大常委会提出的意见和建议，进一步完善&ldquo;一区多园&rdquo;建设、新农村建设和水利建设工作，为促进嘉鱼建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城奠定扎实的基础。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">李鹏谋要求县人大常委会全体组成人员在今后的工作中，要注重自身学习，加强理论休养，更好地指导工作实践；要坚定政治方向，使人大更好地服从和服务于全县工作大局；要提高履职能力，深入调查研究，敢于发表意见；要树立良好形象，加强自身建设，自觉遵纪守法，保持廉洁自律，维护集体团结。</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-21/b8818a1accaca7923f53ef2a77371999.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议现场</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: center; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1192','6','刘蒙、罗阳春','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-21/0b1b27ddbd39eac5ed2b2b31ae979770.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">参观四邑新村建设现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;新农村建设不是建几栋房屋就了事，更重要的是通过新农村建设使农民致富。&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">21</span>日，县委、县政府在潘家湾镇召开四邑村新农村建设专题会议，帮扶该村进行新农村建设的联乐集团董事长周明炎在会上阐明的观点得到与会人员的认可。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">四邑村是周明炎的家乡，为了回报社会，造福家乡父老，周明炎决定依托联乐集团帮扶村里进行迁村腾地，建设四邑新村，并且发展产业，带动村民致富，壮大集体经济。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在四邑新村建设现场，与会人员看到，第一期<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">106</span>户村民的新房主体工程已完工，一排排新居后面<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2500</span>平米的新农村活动中心土地平整已完成。千亩苗木基地已种植苗木<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">800</span>亩，万亩竹柳基地已平整，其中<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5000</span>亩的江滩地已经开始植树。此外还了解到，该村计划打造无公害蔬菜基地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>亩，其中<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>亩的大棚样板已经成功，鱼塘改造、农家乐等项目列入了二期计划。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇在会上说，召开此次会议是对今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span>日我县新农村建设专题会上所部署的工作进行&ldquo;回头看&rdquo;，也是为了研究解决四邑村在新农村建设中所遇到的问题和困难，以进一步推动该村新农村建设工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇指出，办好一个新农村建设的示范点很不容易，必须要一届接着一届干才能出成效，并且就&ldquo;为什么要办点&rdquo;、&ldquo;怎样办点&rdquo;、&ldquo;办什么样的点&rdquo;作了具体要求。他说，办好新农村建设示范点是统筹城乡发展的需要、是展示嘉鱼形象的需要、是引领示范的需要。我县要坚持政府主导、农民主体、企业主力和部门主动的原则，既要建好新农村，也要发展新产业、树立新风尚。各部门要想办法、讲方法，整合项目，安排好实施计划，编制好整村推进的总体规划，努力将四邑村建设成为新农村建设的示范点、农村旅游的新亮点和现代农业的样板点。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委副书记、县长余珂在会上要求，四邑村新农村建设要与致富产业结合，与群众文化生活结合，不仅让农民有新房住，还要让农民腰包鼓起来。各部门要将支持新农村建设作为自身的一项本职工作，支持该村完善规划，完善功能，将该村建设得档次更高、亮点更亮。余珂还安排部署了各部门的具体工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县领导李国光、魏朝东、许标、朱从钦、魏萍出席会议。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-21/28cfba95bf01815ae9d24cdc0bb94a95.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1193','8','嘉鱼县房地产管理局','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">今定于二０一一年十二月二十三日上午九时在司法局六楼招标办公室举行嘉鱼县第三、四期廉租房公开电脑随机摇号仪式。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">特此公告</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"right\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: right; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">嘉鱼县房地产管理局</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"right\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: right; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">二０一一年十二月十六日</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"right\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: right; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"right\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: right; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"right\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: right; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1194','6','聂莉','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" day=\\\\\"21\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">21</span>日下午</st1:chsdate>，副县长魏萍一行来到高铁岭镇，就该镇&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动开展情况进行调研。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">魏萍一行先后深入该镇白果树村、临江村、石泉村和八斗角村，实地查看塘堰改造情况，一路上一片热火朝天的施工景象。在八斗角村，魏萍对塘堰周围的绿化、护栏安装和村容村貌整治情况表示满意。当得知该镇通过&ldquo;四个结合&rdquo;抓&ldquo;三万&rdquo;，做到塘堰改造覆盖自然湾时，对其前阶段的&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动成果给予了充分肯定。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">魏萍要求该镇将&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动与项目建设、新农村建设、社会治安、文化建设相结合，有特色、有规划、有行动。她要求该镇下一阶段继续抓住晴好天气，抢进度、抢时间完成塘堰改造；落实好改造后塘堰的管护工作；同时认真做好前阶段&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的工作小结，推出&ldquo;高铁经验&rdquo;。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据悉，该镇今年共整治塘堰<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">254</span>口，其中结合土地整理项目建设，完工塘堰<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">144</span>口。本次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动整治<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">90</span>口，群众自发清理<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>口。另外，结合新农村建设，新栽树木<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>棵，安装护栏<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"1200\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1200</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>，整治清理村庄<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>处。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
